# Dependencies
**/node_modules/

# Build outputs
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.cache/

# Track frontend build output in this repository
!coordify/dist/
!coordify/dist/**

# Logs
**/*.log

# OS/editor files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/.vscode/

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.env
**/*.env.*

# Markdown files
**/*.md

# Frontend archived docs
coordify/docs/archive/

# README files (workspace-wide)
**/README
**/README.*
**/readme
**/readme.*

# Keep only this top-level project README tracked
!README.md

# Coverage
coverage
